{"id":232967337,"title":"#請益 文書筆電選擇 預算3w","content":"目前有2個選手\n\n1. Acer Swift 5 SF514-54GT （i5-1035G1）\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/1cf908c8-04fb-470e-847f-64787100ba7b/1280.jpeg\n\n2. Asus Vivobook S14 （i5-10210U）有考慮升到i7\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9c1935f1-fa0d-484b-a5a7-0697451273ea/1280.jpeg\n\n\n我前個電腦是macbook pro 2014\n因為沒有用過這兩個牌子所以不知道怎麼選擇\n\n對於acer的i5-1035G1處理器很心動\n但也聽說過很多acer的電池續航力很差而且買幾個月就會開始衰退很嚴重⋯ 相對好像asus比較穩定但處理器效能普普？\n\n想盡量輕一點1.2-1.3kg是極限（因為實驗室比較遠要背著很重QQ），14吋，電池續航力6hrs左右就足夠，不會玩遊戲也不會用電腦看影片，想單純買來幫助課業上的文書資料處理🙏🏼\n\n希望可以有人給點意見QQ","excerpt":"目前有2個選手，1. Acer Swift 5 SF514-54GT （i5-1035G1），2. Asus Vivobook S14 （i5-10210U）有考慮升到i7，我前個電腦是macbook","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"0e0bc27b-8c69-4149-b229-04e7a865a09d","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-27T13:06:21.234Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T15:53:03.527Z","commentCount":13,"likeCount":4,"tags":[],"topics":["筆電","選擇","文書","Win10"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"3C","forumAlias":"3c","school":"長庚大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":4}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/1cf908c8-04fb-470e-847f-64787100ba7b/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9c1935f1-fa0d-484b-a5a7-0697451273ea/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"949356a5-de00-4211-9908-4ad8a0e8a6be","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/1cf908c8-04fb-470e-847f-64787100ba7b/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/1cf908c8-04fb-470e-847f-64787100ba7b/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/1cf908c8-04fb-470e-847f-64787100ba7b/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-